  "instructions": [
    "Heat a large non-stick skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Brush the skillet with 1 tablespoon of olive oil.",
    "Add the minced garlic and saut\b until fragrant.",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, paprika, salt, and black pepper. Cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the chickpea flour and stir for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the folding dough and stir until combined.",
    "Form the mixture into a flat sheet and cook for 2-3 minutes per side, until golden brown and crispy.",
    "Transfer the fold to a plate and sprinkle with chopped parsley and red pepper flakes to taste.",
    "If using feta cheese, crumble it on top of the fold.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
